Jaffy’s Mallaig Kippers Awarded ‘Best Scottish Speciality’

   image

   At a glittering Great Taste Awards ceremony in London last week, Jaffys
   Mallaig Kippers - produced by J Lawrie & Sons - were crowned ‘Best
   Scottish Speciality’.

   Great Taste Awards

   The awards were held at the Royal Garden Hotel in London and are linked
   to the Speciality & Fine Food Fair London which is the leading UK trade
   show for artisan food and drink producers.

   In addition to sponsoring the Best Scottish Speciality award within the
   Great Taste Awards, Scotland Food & Drink was also pleased to assist
   Scottish producers throughout the Speciality & Fine Food Fair by
   hosting stands in the ‘Scotland, Land of Food & Drink’ pavilion.

   Scotland Food & Drink should also like to congratulate all other
   Scottish companies who achieved Gold Stars in the Great Taste Awards –
   a full list can be found on the Great Taste Awards website (see link
   below).

   More information:
     * J. Lawrie & Sons
     * Great Taste Awards

