   Portrait/Logo
   Welcome to our Scottish Food blog. At Scottish Food we are passionate
   about the produce of Scotland, the outstanding and unrivaled
   wholesomeness and quality of Scotland's fare.
   We pay great attention to seasonality of produce and provide
   information and recipes for ingredients when they are at their very
   best. We look at home growing and foraging and also add a sprinkling of
   the culture and history of Scotland, almost always with an angle on
   food and drink.
   Within this blog you will find a wealth of useful information and
   helpful links. Please drop in regularly, you will always find something
   tasty inside.
